::Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer::

"We crashed," Cledar replies, "We escaped in pods, but I never tracked the ship to see if it made it."

He holds out his hand for a handshake. "Its nice to meet all of you."

Rixer, Forrior, and Blyer also step forward, moving to shake hands with the other Maximals.
